<h1 style="line-height: 2.4; margin-top: 20pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 20pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">1 Introduction</span></h1>
<p style="line-height: 2.4; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">This section will provide a general introduction to this project, the functional requirements, its scope, and an overview of the SRS document as a whole.</span></p>
<h2 style="line-height: 2.4; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">1.1 General Description</span></h2>
<p style="line-height: 2.4; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&ldquo;NuFu&rdquo; is a subscription based media streaming service which charges a $10/monthly base fee for access to 10 show slots (access to ten series). Additional slots thereafter will come in at an additional $1.50 per slot and any movie can be rented for $0.50 for 24 hours. The passages below discuss the functions and details for the website which will serve as the platform for the &ldquo;NuFu&rdquo; streaming service. &nbsp;</span></p>
<h2 style="line-height: 2.4; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">1.2 Functional Requirements</span></h2>
